{
  "texts": [
    "Viknesh et al.",
    "[55] provides a computer-aided detection method for melanoma early diagnosis and therapy.",
    "Two methods are suggested in this work for the detection of skin cancer.",
    "In the first technique, transfer learning methods, such as the AlexNet, LeNet, and VGG-16 models are used for the diagnosis of skin cancer.",
    "Furthermore, they investigate how different dataset sizes relate to the model's depth and performance."
  ]
}